snippet.title: Tents and Trees - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Tents and Trees, the puzzle game set in the great outdoors, is coming to Nintendo Switch™!

#NintendoSwitch #tentsandtrees #puzzlegame #announcement #trailer #gaming #frozax

Get ready to pitch your tent, as the peaceful universe of Tents and Trees is making its way to Nintendo Switch!

(PEGI version)
